## 📋 CLI Commands

### Key Management

```bash
# Generate new Kyber key
quantum-refiner keys generate-kyber [--key-id ID] [--expires-days N] [--rotate-days N]

# Generate new Dilithium key
quantum-refiner keys generate-dilithium [--key-id ID] [--expires-days N] [--rotate-days N]

# List all keys
quantum-refiner keys list-keys

# Rotate key
quantum-refiner keys rotate-key KEY_ID
```

### Dataset Operations

```bash
# Encrypt dataset
quantum-refiner dataset encrypt DATASET_PATH DATASET_NAME [--kyber-key ID] [--dilithium-key ID]

# Decrypt dataset
quantum-refiner dataset decrypt DATASET_NAME OUTPUT_PATH KYBER_KEY_ID --dilithium-public-key HEX

# Get dataset info (without decrypting)
quantum-refiner dataset info DATASET_NAME
```

### Integrity Verification

```bash
# Verify complete dataset
quantum-refiner verify dataset-integrity DATASET_NAME --dilithium-public-key HEX
```

### Training

```bash
# Run secure training demo
quantum-refiner train demo DATASET_NAME KYBER_KEY_ID [--batch-size N] [--epochs N]
```

### Audit & Monitoring

```bash
# Show audit logs
quantum-refiner audit logs

# System status
quantum-refiner status

# Version info
quantum-refiner version
```

