# Test 2: Tampering Detection  
# Modified ciphertext fails GCM authentication

# Test 3: Nonce Uniqueness
# Same plaintext produces different ciphertexts

# Test 4: Hybrid Encryption Completeness
# Both Kyber and AES needed for full confidentiality
```

