## 📊 Compliance & Standards

### NIST Post-Quantum Cryptography Standards

- **FIPS 203**: Module-Lattice-Based Key-Encapsulation Mechanism (Kyber)
- **FIPS 204**: Module-Lattice-Based Digital Signature Algorithm (Dilithium)
- **FIPS 197**: Advanced Encryption Standard (AES-256)
- **FIPS 180-4**: SHA Hash Standard (SHA-256)

### Implementation

- **liboqs-python**: NIST-approved, NCC Group audited PQC library
- **cryptography.io**: FIPS 140-2 compliant backend for AES
- **PBKDF2**: NIST SP 800-132 KDF

### Regulatory Alignment

- **NIST Roadmap**: On track for National Security Memorandum (NSM-10) compliance
- **EU Cryptography Regulation**: Supports quantum-safe migration
- **Industry Standards**: Aligned with ETSI QSC white papers

